               mit dirr un </origDate></creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><facsimile><surface><graphic url="http://images.monasterium.net/pics/AT-WStLA/HA-U/WStLA-HA-Priv_14_r.jpg"/></surface><surface><graphic url="http://images.monasterium.net/pics/AT-WStLA/HA-U/WStLA-HA-Priv_14_v.jpg"/></surface></facsimile><text><body><div type="abstract" resp="lp"><p><rs type="event" ref="#ev__QGW_II_I_625"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__rudolf_iv_herzog_von_oesterreich_QGW_II_I_769"><roleName type="title">Erzherzog</roleName> Rudolf IV.</rs></rs>
